Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.18,0:00:55.73,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\be2}不要那麼溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.82,0:00:59.36,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\be2}這樣又會相互傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.43,0:01:06.35,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\be2}堆積的謊言已經讓我無法動彈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.55,0:01:10.07,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\be2}雖然想要立刻去見你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.16,0:01:13.66,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\be2}卻找不到藉口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.73,0:01:18.79,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\be2}即使是在最後一頁
